ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to (1) address the error raised by the Standing Joint Committee on the Scrutiny of Regulations and to meet the requirement of section 5(2) of the Immigration and Refugee Protection Act; (2) make a technical revision to an element of section 13.11 of the Regulations to ensure grammatical accuracy.
